name: Creature Hunters
description: Creature Hunters is a play to earn defense NFT Game. It is a blockchain-based online game based on NFT. Creature Hunters is built using a combination of NFT and the technology of each item, each of which has its own set of abilities. With easy access to all NFTs, users can manage and trade their total value in the NFT market. Furthermore, they are able to create, buy, sell, exchange, farm, and use NFTs with ease.
